SpiffGIS is currently nothing more than a GeoTools LAB build on the tutorials 
here: http://docs.geotools.org. Its implimented using the Netbeans Platform
and build using maven.

Add the following proxy repository to your Nexus proxy if your using one:

Repository ID: osgeo
Repository Name: Open Source Geospatial Foundation Repository
Repository Type: proxy
Repository Policy: Release
Repository Format: maven2
Contained in groups: 
   Public Repositories
Remote URL: http://download.osgeo.org/webdav/geotools/


